T1  - The Effect of Social Interaction on Economic Transactions: Evidence from Changes in Two Retail Formats
AU  - Goldfarb, Avi
AU  - McDevitt, Ryan C.
AU  - Samila, Sampsa
AU  - Silverman, Brian S.
Y1  - 2015/02/13
